            <div class='dropdown-header'>Finance Topics</div>
            <a class='dropdown-topic' href='/search/label/Investing'>Investing<small>Analysis &amp; guides</small></a>
            <a class='dropdown-topic' href='/search/label/Personal+Finance'>Personal Finance<small>Practical how-tos</small></a>
